## Next Steps for Deployment
To complete the Speed Insights setup, the following steps need to be performed in the Vercel dashboard:
1. Enable Speed Insights in the project settings
2. Deploy the application to Vercel
3. Verify the `/_vercel/speed-insights/script.js` script is loaded
4. View metrics in the Speed Insights dashboard after users visit the site

## Technical Notes
- This is a React + TypeScript + Vite project
- The project already had Vercel Analytics configured, making the Speed Insights addition straightforward
- Speed Insights will automatically track Core Web Vitals and other performance metrics
- The component is framework-aware and optimized for React applications
